<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bill_of_lading&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="references-small"></div>
<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
